City Hallwill be lit Blue and Green to support RSPCA Million Paws Walk.

The annual RSPCA Million Paws Walk (now in it&#39;s 30th year) raises awareness and funds for the vital work RSPCA QLD does in preventing cruelty to animals.&nbsp;

This Light Up is organised by: RSPCA Qld

