The Reddacliff Place sculptureswill be lit LGTB Rainbow to celebrate IDAHOBIT.

Brisbane City Council - River City Pride &nbsp;wants to light up Brisbane in celebration and awareness of IDAHOBIT Day 2023. &nbsp;On May 17, 1990 - the World Health Organization removed homosexuality from the Classification of Diseases and Related Health Problems. While we celebrate this milestone and other advancements in LGBTQIA+ equality, the unfortunate reality is that there&#39;s still more work to do.

This Light Up is organised by: Brisbane City Council - River City Pride&nbsp;

